Titolo: Heir of Zendor

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Heir of Zendor: The Legend and The Land, released in Japan as Gotha II, is a strategy video game developed by Micronet and published by Koei. It is the sequel to Gotha: Ismailia Seneki. It was an exclusive for the Sega Saturn in North America, while in Japan it also appeared on the PlayStation.